                        '⚠️ <strong>On that new tab, click the "AI Recorder" bookmark now</strong> — nothing is captured until you do. ' +
                        'A red REC badge in the top-right of that page confirms it worked.';
                } else {
                    hint.innerHTML =
                        '🟢 Recording is live, but no <code>url=</code> is set in config.properties, so no tab was opened automatically.<br>' +
                        '⚠️ Open your target site yourself, then <strong>click the "AI Recorder" bookmark on that tab</strong> before doing anything else.';
                }
            })
            .catch(() => {
